import jax.numpy as jnp

def generated_fn(x0, x1, x2):

    v1 = jnp.cos(x2)
    v2 = jnp.minimum(x1, v1)
    v3 = jnp.minimum(x1, v0)
    v4 = jnp.sin(v3)
    v5 = jnp.maximum(x0, x2)
